OL,5, Grand Slam-winning rugby captain Ryan  
OL,6, Jones has joined a legal action against
OL,7, rugby's governing bodies after being   
OL,8, diagnosed with early onset dementia.   
OL,10,FIn an interview with the Sunday Times  
OL,11,Fthe 41-year-old former Wales and       
OL,12,FBritish Lions forward said he felt like
OL,13,Fhis "world was falling apart".         
OL,15,FIn December, rugby World Cup winner,   
OL,16,FSteve Thompson and seven other former  
OL,17,Fplayers started the claim.             
OL,19,FWorld Rugby said it constantly strived 
OL,20,F"to safeguard and support our players".
